inspectomop.results.Results.fetchmany¶

Results.fetchmany(size=None)¶

Fetch many rows.

When all rows are exhausted, returns an empty sequence.

This method is provided for backwards compatibility with SQLAlchemy 1.x.x.

To fetch rows in groups, use the _engine.Result.partitions() method.

Returns:

a sequence of _engine.Row objects.

See also

_engine.Result.partitions()
